      "specificArticles": [
        {
          "text": "Rosia Montana is the oldest locality from Romania, it has an unique mining and cultural landscape and it's situated in the Transylvania mountains, a perfect place for mountain biking or hiking. The package <b>includes 2 nights accommodation and a guided trail (~6h) to the main cultural and natural attractions.</b>"
        }
      ]
