          "text": "<b><i class='far fa-clock'></i> 09:00 - 15:00 - Guided trail of the main cultural and natural objectives</b>. Will start from the historic center, where will visit some patrimony buildings (multicultural churches and schools or the goldsmith houses) built by various nations who came here to extract gold. Will continue with the Cârnic massif where will visit some natural and mining objectives (pounds, protected areas, open pits and gold galleries).",
